In [12]:
#spatial points (unprojected)
seaports=gpd.GeoDataFrame(data=infoseaports.copy(),
                           geometry=gpd.points_from_xy(infoseaports.Longitude,
                                                       infoseaports.Latitude),
                          crs=4326)# notice it is unprojected

# keep Brazil
seaports_peru=seaports[seaports['Country Code']=='Peru'].copy()

# reset indexes
seaports_peru.reset_index(drop=True, inplace=True)

# reprojecting
seaports_peru_24891=seaports_peru.to_crs(24891) # projected crs
